  <title>Windows Phone SmsComposeTask Kullanımı (Uygulama'dan SMS yollama)</title>
  <description>Windows Phone'da uygulama i&amp;ccedil;erisinden SMS g&amp;ouml;ndermek istediğinizde&amp;nbsp;SmsComposeTask&amp;nb</description>
  <content>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Windows Phone'da uygulama i&amp;ccedil;erisinden SMS g&amp;ouml;ndermek istediğinizde&amp;nbsp;SmsComposeTask&amp;nbsp;kontrol&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml; kullanabilirsiniz. Daha &amp;ouml;ncesinde geliştirmiş olduğum &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.windowsphone.com/tr-tr/store/app/kandil-bayram-sms/555f4902-7aad-4b63-a614-30bba788ae11"&gt;Kandil,Bayram SMS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; uygulamasında da kullandığım kodlar aşağıda mevcuttur.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="brush:csharp;auto-links:false;toolbar:false" contenteditable="false"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; SmsComposeTask myTask= new SmsComposeTask();
&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; myTask.To = " "; &amp;nbsp;//Sms'in g&amp;ouml;nderileceği numara
&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;myTask.Body &amp;nbsp;="Message"; &amp;nbsp;//Sms'in i&amp;ccedil;eriği
&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;myTask.Show();&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;//Task'i &amp;ccedil;alıştırdığımız yer&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
